data.description: If your looking for peace and tranquility this home is for you.  2017 manufactured home w/1512 sq ft home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath rooms, primary bedroom w/large walk in closet, separate utility room, enjoy the spacious floor plan, large kitchen, eating bar & w/walk in pantry with plenty of storage, lots of counter space and dining area.  This home is very private with 1.46 acres overlooking the Saulk River and beautiful mountain views. Nice level lot, with propane heating, wired for a generator, RV parking, fire pit area, garden area, out building and pump house. There is room to build a nice shop.  This home is ready to become your own retreat.
